At the bottom of the Command Center is a row of panels from which you may access information about our systems and resources.  Information about Rebel-controlled resources, as reported by our field personnel, may also be accessed.  These 'Finders' include (from left to right): the System Finder (locates known systems by name), the Fleet Finder (locates fleets or ships), the Troop Finder (locates troops), and the Personnel Finder (locates characters and special forces).  Click on any of these consoles to view the information contained therein.